{
  "transcript_id": "10353.5",
  "source_file": "10353.5.json",
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "chunk_words_setting": 800,
  "n_chunks": 3,
  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for the American Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made my way in with the American Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- I worked my way up.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked for the 97th Signal Company till-- for almost a year.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in-- I was charge in the mess hall.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given the duty-- first of all, the stockroom.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They keep track of the-- of the rations to allocate the food for the daily need for the kitchen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to-- and then, later on, to write up the requisitions that were needed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For about eight months, I stayed with them, because they eventually evacuated.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Camp Wels was evacuated.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taken into Linz, L-I-N-Z, Austria.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were giving some more substantial lodging.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The, the American government, military government expropriated a huge-- a huge block-- or blocks, I should say, of apartments that they allocated to the former concentration camp inmates.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there they were-- they were governed under the UNRRA at that time-- U-N-R-A-- and also the Joint-- the American Joint Distribution Committee.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, the UNRRA was transferred over to the IRO, to the International Refugee Organization.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I stayed in Wels.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the camp was evacuated.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I got to be very well known in the-- in the camp because, every night, I took-- you know the Americans, how generous they are with, with dishing out food and how much waste there is when we weren't used to it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So me being in charge, more or less, in the mess hall, I told my mess sergeant-- who incidentally was Jewish.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him, look, there is a camp here, you know, with some poor people from the concentration camp.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- why throw out all this food?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anything that's left over, let's take it over to-- to the camp.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, I was allowed to wear American uniform, military uniform.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I drove-- we drove into the camp every night.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took in the leftovers, whatever there was.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we gave it to them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they knew me as the American that's coming.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The American is-- this is how I got to know my wife, too.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when they evacuated the camp from Wels, I lost track with them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was in January of 1946 that I had nothing to do in Wels.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was the only Jew there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe there was the two tailors and a barber that was-- stayed on.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went into Linz to see my old buddies there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I visited my wife.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one thing led to another.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before too long, we got married.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On January 27, we got married.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I gave notice to the Signal Company.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told them that I'm-- I stayed on for a while, but not for too long.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I moved into Linz.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Linz, I went into the 14th Regulating Station of the Transportation Corps.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I presented myself as a knowledgeable person running a mess hall.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was immediately hired.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was another division of the USA forces.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in charge.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our, our-- we were in charge of anything that was moving.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything mechanical moving on the surface, or in the air had to get our permission.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It came from our headquarters.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were the headquarters there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I worked there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was given the duty of supervising the five mess halls and to do the requisitions for them, to make up the menus for them on daily basis.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this had to be done per capita.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, you-- but we ran a very, very model operation, so much so that we were-- we were commended.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were visited by many officers from different regions, too.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there till 1948, till June or July 1948, at which time I gave it up because the inspections became too frequent.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very strenuous.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to be on your toes all the time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, you couldn't have your-- your rations had to balance to the T all the time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to do something about it, you know, to hide things.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it became very strenuous.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I gave it up.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I worked for the AJDC for about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] five months, I would say-- five or six months.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was their representative in Camp Steyr.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the social worker at--",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the Joint representative in Camp Steyr.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was traveling from Linz to Steyr on daily basis.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My office was, was in Steyr.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Joint's duty-- your-- you know-- we were-- we were given the task to look after all the Romanian refugees that came across.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to come across from [INAUDIBLE], from the Russian-dominated side, sector, into the American sector.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were given the task to look after those people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they come through there, they should be fed.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they should be given, if necessary, some clothing, whatever they needed.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Put them onto a truck, and to ship them further.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They went either to Salzburg, or-- and from Salzburg, they went to Italy or to Munich.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, they were dispersed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, I made some great efforts to get into-- to the United States.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But just to backtrack a little bit, I still didn't know anything that I had a sur-- another surviving sister.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know-- I knew that I had two surviving sisters, one in Israel and the one that was in hiding.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the third one, I didn't know what happened to her.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But in June of 1945-- or July.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I believe it was July, because in July, I found out that she was somewhere in a hospital in Germany because she was very sick.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then in August, I under-- I got word that she came back to my hometown, to Satu Mare.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that she eventually married my pre-war brother-in-law, who lost his wife and six children in, in Auschwitz.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She never came back.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so he married her.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Eventually, they wanted to leave Romania as well.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they came to Vienna.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from Vienna-- by that time, I was very well connected with the Brihah.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had them come over to the American side.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I arranged for all their papers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Eventually-- they stayed with-- with me for about almost a year.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they decided that they want to do something for themselves.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they made tracks first to Paris, France.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I made sure that my sister was taken across the German border.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They went to France.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They stayed in Paris several months.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And from Paris, they went to Israel.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In Israel, they-- it was a very bad time in 1948.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't have to tell you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He is a master craftsman in bookbinding.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he eventually-- he opened up a-- a fair-size bookbinding factory.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they re-established the family.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They have two boys.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As for myself, I got married and-- on January 27th.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went through the-- the regular life.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had the requisition put in for admission to the United States.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had some great pull.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My commanding officer kind of took me personally down to the American consulate.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have some terrific credentials that I, I can show.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the American Immigration was very slow in, in granting a, a visa.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, a commission came out from Canada that they were recruiting furriers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got word.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got word that I should register all those furriers in Camp Steyr that desired to immigrate to Canada, which I did.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I registered 14 of 'em.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the day came when the commission was to sit in Linz to examine these people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was to take them in and to present them to the commission.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by that time, my superior was a Scottish lady who was working for the IRO.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was sitting at the table with one member of the commission.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was presenting the furriers, the applicants, one by one, I sort of bent over to her-- and I forgot her name-- Miss So-And-So.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, what do you think?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Should I put in an application for-- to Canada?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, sure, go.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a very nice country.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm not a furrier.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the man from the commission was sitting there, who was a Jewish fellow.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said-- she bent to him.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, this man is a very good man.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He worked for us, you know.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, he would like to go to Canada.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he turns to me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, well, are you a furrier?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, uh, no.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, do you have any relatives in Canada?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says, I don't.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my wife has.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Who are they?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ladowsky, they have a restaurant.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As it happens, they have a very famous restaurant in Toronto, whom he knew very well.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, Ladowsky is the relative?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, OK.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, you have to go through an examination.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You think you can do it?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I says, I'll try.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know something about what furriers do.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when I came to the officials from the IRO and they said, are you a furrier?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What can you do?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm a blocker.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now a blocker-- they didn't have-- they had facilities.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had sewing machines.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had hand sewing.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't-- didn't have facilities to-- to test blockers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, I'm a blocker.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, you're a blocker?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Good.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stamped.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Good.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went through all the rigmarole with all the examination with the Canadian officials, with, you know, political, and literacy, and health, you name it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Health",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we finally got the visa to go to Canada.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in October-- on October 1948, we arrived into Canada after a horrendous voyage that we had.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My wife was, at that time, five months pregnant.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my first son was born in Canada in February of 1949.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Straight to Toronto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived there ever since.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were received exceedingly well.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we went into-- our first station was to go into the restaurant to have breakfast.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole gang in my group was to come into that restaurant-- that was sponsored also by the Federation-- to have breakfast in her relatives' restaurant.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very well received.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us into their house.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed with them for some length of time till we acquired our own place.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got a job as a shipper in a ladies coat and suit factory that also belonged to a relative of my wife's.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after a short while, having had the experience in the textile industry, a textile sales-- salesman, I made myself rather useful.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before too long, I got, little by little, promoted.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a second son.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in 1956, I left my position.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I established my own business.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had a factory with partners.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We employed, at one time, close to 100 people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in 1986, after 30 years being in business, I retired.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we live in Toronto.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, thank you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, two reasons.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I was rather young.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 20 years old.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are certain things, like for instance, when we arrived in Bernau, there was no more train.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to go through the mountains.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- I slept-- overnight, I slept on the ground.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was freezing cold.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I survived, you know.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in Bergen-Belsen, I lost my shoes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I walked in the snow.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I survived.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't catch a cold.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we hope-- although death or-- was hovering over us and, we-- more or less, in the back of our mind, we didn't think that we will survive.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we-- on the other part of the brain told us that we will survive, and we, we, we will come out of it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- And then it probably-- we didn't quite comprehend the, the gravity of the, of the situation that we were in.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We knew that it's bad.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We knew-- we saw all the corpses that were taken away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We saw they were-- they were dropping out.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But somehow, we, we had the feeling that we will make it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I-- I'll never forget the one situation when the Swedish Red Cross made an inspection in Bergen-Belsen at our camp.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the rumor was going around that there is a commission from Sweden here.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I met one of the guys that was coming from the washroom.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he used the expression-- he says, the commission is here.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It looks like maybe after all, we are not going to perish.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was his remark, which was quite an expression.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But that was the general feeling, that we were ready to perish.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But nonetheless, we survived.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we, we did.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one, one place-- at one time, we thought that we are for sure condemned.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other hand, there was that spark, spark of hope that, that we nurtured.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would like them to know of what we went through.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And that it should never happen again.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKS] It was-- it was a period of history that is really written in blood.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they should know that, despite everything, we maintained our heritage and that we should conserve it and keep it forever.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This picture was taken in Linz, Austria.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was taken in my-- at the end of 1947.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was employed that time at the American Occupation Forces.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a rather good life by that time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we bounced back.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived a very acceptable and comfortable life, as you can see.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's my wife [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that is hanging onto my right.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- at that time, I was going into 24-- 24 years old.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were reasonably satisfied by that time, except for the memories that we had to carry along with us.",
